data.description: This Charming Updated 3bd/1.5ba Colonial Features a Newer Furnace w/ Central Air, Newer Windows Throughout, Updated Electrical and Plumbing, Newer Two Car Garage, and much more! The Beautifully Updated Kitchen has Plenty of Cabinet and Countertop Space! Newer Fridge and Gas Range! Large Finished Basement with Glass Block Windows, Laundry Room w/ Epoxy Coated Floor, and Additional Storage Rooms. Newer Carpet and Refinished Hardwood Floors Throughout. Three Bedrooms on the 2nd w/ Nicely Updated Full Bath. 1/2 Bath on 1st. Minutes to Cleveland Clinic, UH, Case, and University Circle. Close to Parks, Shopping, places of worship, and Dining. Americas Preferred Home Warranty is included on this property for 1yr truly no worries! Call for your private showing today!
